words.context: If the @Profile annotation is omitted, registration will occur regardless of which (if any) profiles are active.

words.note:
1.VERB 省略；删节；排除；遗漏
Our apologies to David Pannick for omitting his name from last week's article.
我们在上周的文章里漏掉了戴维·潘尼克的名字，特此向他致歉。
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.VERB 未（做）；没有（做）
His new girlfriend had omitted to tell him she was married.
他的新女友未把自己已婚的事实告诉他。
